 in february  polycom acquired accord networks which offered the mgc line in october  it acquired picturetel polycom digital tabletop microphone with mute button in  polycom introduced its first high definition video conferencing system soon after it announced the polycom realpresence experience rpx immersive telepresence solution a roomwithinaroom telepresence environment based on the design by destiny conferencing formerly telesuites which polycom acquired  in january  in february  the firm introduced a new bridge platform called rmx  designed to support high definition and telepresence applications it also expanded its telepresence and hd video product lines in  with the polycom telepresence experience solutions and new executive desktop solutions expanded its line of roombased conference rooms in  polycom delivered the polycom converged management application cma a video network and system management application for provisioning and managing video networks the cma includes an application for broadscale desktop video called cma desktop later that year the firm introduced the distributed media application dma  a networkbased application that manages and distributes multipoint video calls within an enterprise network environment toward the end of  polycom also announced its plans to support higher resolution – p and p at  frames per second same frame rate as tv – across its visual communication product line endpoints telepresence solutions and infrastructure solutions during  the firm introduced a new immersive telepresence solution the polycom open telepresence experience otx  providing collaboration including p using half the bandwidth of other comparable systems polycom audio and voiceedit polycom soundstation ip  sip conference phone the first soundstation conference phone shipped in  the original device was followed by versions offering extended performance soundstation premier premier satellite soundstation ex the soundstation first shipped internationally to the uk in  followed by other products and an expanding list of countries the soundstation was superseded by the soundstation  in  when att discontinued its dspa processor on which the original machine was based due to technological advancements during the nearly year period the soundstation  exhibited more features and sound transparency although still limited to  khz audio bandwidth due to its conventional analog pots connection it was supplemented by the soundstation w wireless speakerphone which was a dect system wdct in north america and by the soundstation vtx wired speakerphone the first such speakerphone capable of  khz audio operation over conventional telephone lines in december  polycom acquired aspi networks a company specializing in installed voice systems polycom worked with a large number of audio visual integrators offering its vortex product in  polycom introduced the vortex successor the polycom soundstructure series in the first quarter of  polycom introduced its first voice over ip conference phone the soundstation ip  in  the soundstation ip  and soundstation ip  models were introduced both offering polycom’s hd voice and acoustic clarity technology in  the firm introduced its first hd voice product the soundstation vtx  conference phone polycom hd voice is wideband audio audio bandwidth extension to    and  khz offering more than twice the clarity of narrowband voice  khz in  polycom introduced its communicator the cs which was the industry’s first wideband speakerphone for a pc in  the firm entered the circuitswitched desktop phone business with a line of its soundpoint phones in the third quarter of  it entered the ip desktop phone business with the soundpoint ip  because it does not manufacture its own call server polycom phones use session initiation protocol sip to connect to more than  different call control platforms today the firm offers a full line of desktop ip phones from the entry level to a color display fullfeatured hd voice first introduced to the soundpoint line in  applicationsenabled phone in  polycom acquired spectralink corp whose product lines consisted of wifi and proprietary wireless telephone systems as well as the kirk digital enhanced cordless telephony dect product line in  polycom added applications enablement to its soundstation and soundpoint ip phones the first product to market was the company’s productivity suite which the company currently offers an open api for thirdparty developers in  the firm introduced two videoenabled products the vvx  business media phone which combines a personal video conferencing system with a voice over ip voip telephone with polycom hd voice and an open application programming interface api and web browser for realtime delivery of personalized web content and integration with business applications it also launched the cx unified conferencing station by licensing the distribution rights for microsoft roundtable in  polycom announced the vvx  a voip business media phone with a gesturebased touchscreen interface and the capability to play fullscreen html video embedded in web pages the vvx  has a x inch display making it smaller than the vvx  in screen size but also in desktop footprint also in  polycom announced that they had shipped their  millionth conference phonecitation needed in  the wifi and dect products were divested to a new company called spectralink referencesedit  polycom reports fourth quarter and fiscal year  earnings – company – polycom polycom inc polycom  retrieved    company overview — polycom inc retrieved  april    httpwwwforbescomsitessarahcohenpolycomrepositioned  a b valuation quirks help end proposed polycommitel merger nytimescom  retrieved    polycom company profile broad connect telecom retrieved  march    polycom inc september   briefmary mcdowell named ceo of polycom effective completing acquisition by siris reuters retrieved august   mary mcdowell named ceo of polycom effective as of the closing of the acquisition 